{"tid":587381,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"睇番上次補選新聞...好感觸","createTime":"2018-03-10T11:26:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-11T03:10:11.000Z","uid":156547,"like":64,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"18a0990e6c2e75ed271bdf2092bb3fa87ff8b466","tid":587381,"uid":156547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T11:26:19.000Z","msg":"聽日投票日，諗番起上次新東補選<br />\n梁天琦由寂寂無名既大學生(所謂暴徒)<br />\n搖身一變政治明日之星<br />\n本土派氛圍前所未有咁高漲，咁有希望<br />\n我當時真係以為天琦講既&quot;三分天下&quot;真係會實現(你可能會笑我天真)<br />\n到今天真本土基本上已經蕩然無存<br />\n望番轉頭，真係好唏噓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4a4f90676c2141f505e36e425082b5efb514386","tid":587381,"uid":50457,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T01:26:37.000Z","msg":"對手係最大的恐怖集團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7db6df80bd974a19006665b7680c4c6f7e4687a","tid":587381,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T01:44:51.000Z","msg":"nothing is true everything is permitted"},{"pid":"461bd8777473fbb6ce1bcbb46bab54669e12abf4","tid":587381,"uid":47359,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T01:47:23.000Z","msg":"但個個含撚去投楊岳橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又話楊岳橋同以前啲泛民係唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bea94d822d459874d3cffa710f1e76d328244be2","tid":587381,"uid":72009,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T01:49:57.000Z","msg":"本土派之後自己搞死自己<br />\n成班柴娃娃抗爭<br />\n有沒有向市民道歉"},{"pid":"762a9fc7d61fe878ca815515ef95500bffb6cdcd","tid":587381,"uid":4618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"461bd8777473fbb6ce1bcbb46bab54669e12abf4","tid":587381,"uid":47359,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T01:47:23.000Z","msg":"但個個